                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">很流畅，可惜只写到东汉建立，简述了刘秀的制度变革。最后几章赶得稍有些粗糙了</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="949844471">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-949844471" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-949844471" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="949844471">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/monsoon/">冬季风</a>
                    <span>2015-08-13</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">读起来不觉得累。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="928174938">
